data.description:
Nice updated 3 bedroom 1 bath in south Austin my manchaca and west William cannon. .can walk to CVS, sprouts ,casa Garcia ...no smokers or pets allowed at all

Utilities are extra. They would be added to the lease each month the bills comes in which would be due at that time as well

Furnished or partially furnished. Tenant can pay for utilities or they can add those to monthly rent when Bill comes, would consider 6 month lease
